Peter Gale was fired from his position at Nonsuch High School for Girls in Cheam, Surrey . 
  He was appointed to run the school in September 2013 after the mysterious departure of Karin Rowsell . 
  His contract was terminated due to 'serious breaches' in safeguarding procedures . 
  Mr Gale was sacked for 'inappropriate' and 'unprofessional' behaviour . 
 